strings.Value: "I saw bird nest on my way. Tender meat... bones go crunch..."
"I caught a rat! Mine! Won't share, don't ask!"
"Yeah, fresh meat would be nice. Too bad nobody hunts today."
"If only my family tutor who nagged me about the importance of each set of cutlery could hear you... yes, wouldn't mind the pleasure of seeing his face at the sound of your babbling!"
"Goblins eat garbage they find. No need to feed you."
"You could survive in the desert, that's for sure!"
"You could survive in the desert, that's for sure!"
